Action Button.

00:03:15.500 --> 00:03:16.494
So I scroll down.

00:03:16.494 --> 00:03:18.660
There's a lot of elements
that are imported already,

00:03:18.660 --> 00:03:20.910
but just right underneath
the Paper toolbar here,

00:03:20.910 --> 00:03:23.180
I'll drop in my own
import for Paper FAB.

00:03:23.180 --> 00:03:28.030
So I can have a little bit of
UI showing up on the screen.

00:03:28.030 --> 00:03:31.020
Next, I'm going to hop
over to my index.html file.

00:03:31.020 --> 00:03:34.372
And in the section that
says "data route home,"

00:03:34.372 --> 00:03:36.580
I'm going to take this
paragraph here and just delete

00:03:36.580 --> 00:03:41.160
it and replace it with my
floating action button.

00:03:41.160 --> 00:03:44.770
So get rid of this p-tag
and drop in that paper FAB

00:03:44.770 --> 00:03:46.090
and give it an icon of Add.

00:03:48.740 --> 00:03:51.412
