00:03:56.420 --> 00:03:58.210
Refresh or anything like that.

00:03:58.210 --> 00:03:59.610
Now, the way that
this is working

00:03:59.610 --> 00:04:01.550
is the Gulp version
of the Starter Kit

00:04:01.550 --> 00:04:03.540
comes with a tool
called Browser Sync,

00:04:03.540 --> 00:04:07.030
and Browser Sync synchronizes
updates to all of your devices

00:04:07.030 --> 00:04:09.170
whenever you save
files in your editor.

00:04:09.170 --> 00:04:13.530
So if I had a phone or a tablet
plugged into my laptop right

00:04:13.530 --> 00:04:15.610
now, I was trying to
debug on all of them once,

00:04:15.610 --> 00:04:18.415
they would all refresh
all at the same instant,

00:04:18.415 --> 00:04:19.290
which is really cool.

