00:06:10.260 --> 00:06:13.820
you had layout attributes that
came bundled with Polymer.

00:06:13.820 --> 00:06:16.100
Those don't seem to be
around in Polymer 1.0,

00:06:16.100 --> 00:06:17.760
so what happened to those?

00:06:17.760 --> 00:06:19.230
Good question, Todd.

00:06:19.230 --> 00:06:22.280
