took all of those classes

00:06:27.750 --> 00:06:29.870
and we bundled them up
into their own element set

00:06:29.870 --> 00:06:31.540
called Iron Flex Layout.

00:06:31.540 --> 00:06:33.810
So you can actually follow
this link right here

00:06:33.810 --> 00:06:36.090
and go to the repo
for Iron Flex Layout.

00:06:36.090 --> 00:06:38.580
