have custom properties

00:06:38.580 --> 00:06:40.310
that you can apply
to your own elements.

00:06:40.310 --> 00:06:42.940
We also have CSS files in
there that you can just

00:06:42.940 --> 00:06:46.690
import into your elements and
use those to get your Flexbox

00:06:46.690 --> 00:06:49.320
layout attributes back, or
layout classes, I should say.

